event.name: Build an API Workshop
event.description: Learn how to build an API in this workshop hosted by ACM Development! At the end of this workshop, you’ll be able to create your own sample API endpoint that accepts your email and returns your name and Discord tag. No prior skills required, so make sure to make it to this event hosted by Harsha Srikara & Eric Zhang! This is a great opportunity for beginners interested in APIs and backend development!
